    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like a losing game though. like i'm just exerting energy to stay in a world that i'm not even built for. i'm so tired of the noise and the constant effort of trying to bridge that gap between me and everyone else. sometimes i just think about what it would be like to not have to try anymore. to just stop the noise.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
